    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/cd76e175f0268b305d18cd7ca9a1ac46.poster.avif?t=1729246034\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/cd76e175f0268b305d18cd7ca9a1ac46.webm?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/cd76e175f0268b305d18cd7ca9a1ac46.mp4?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>猫在阳光中静静眨着眼时，到底在想什么？鱼骨架？毛球？不，是大屠杀。彻彻底底的大屠杀。人类朋友，快来选择你的小猫咪，逗弄这破坏之王，看看这些淘气包怎么炸毛嘶吼。一切尽在《Heist Kitty：猫城风云》。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/c234a39c3898fe7b7da598219a07d25b.poster.avif?t=1729246034\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/c234a39c3898fe7b7da598219a07d25b.webm?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/c234a39c3898fe7b7da598219a07d25b.mp4?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多玩家猫咪混战</h2>还有比满屋猫咪更让人崩溃的事吗*？有，全城都是猫。在这款开放世界的多玩家（猫砂盒）沙盒游戏中肆意破坏，透过桀骜不驯的小猫之眼来观察生活。你可以选择独自行动，也可以呼朋引伴，一起狂野：在舞池中大显身手，进入游乐场夺取高手，或劫持车辆，呼啸着穿越城市的大街。 <br>*别担心，没有猫受到伤害。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/57406107db4d3238e785c35b3c4655d8.poster.avif?t=1729246034\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/57406107db4d3238e785c35b3c4655d8.webm?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/57406107db4d3238e785c35b3c4655d8.mp4?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你会选择站在哪一边？</h2>欢迎来到猫咪之城。在这里，毛乍局长手下的猫警队正与诡计多端的黑爪帮斗智斗勇，希望能压制住狸子·卡塔泰利的势力。但是事情并不能如局长所愿。要想关住这些为非作歹的猫，就像牛栏关猫仔——没用。去街上吧，当个警喵，或者为黑爪帮卖命。无论你站在法律的哪一边，你势必都会过上炸毛怒吼的混乱生活。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/800888cbaa5f6fbe441e0d7f76e8182b.poster.avif?t=1729246034\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/800888cbaa5f6fbe441e0d7f76e8182b.webm?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/800888cbaa5f6fbe441e0d7f76e8182b.mp4?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成为终极淘气猫</h2>如果你是一只循规蹈矩的猫，那你就长歪了。无论你走到哪里，都要在身后留下一个烂摊子。把杯子推下桌；在杂货店大肆破坏；运用人类亲手打造的复杂武器对他们发动出人意料的突然攻击。不用担心后果，因为在猫咪的世界里，没有“后果”这个词。",
